title: WSL fixture against Brighton rescheduled
body_text:
Our Barclays Women's Super League against Brighton & Hove Albion has been rescheduled for Wednesday 10 May.
The match will take place at the Broadfield Stadium and will kick off at 7:30pm (UK).
All tickets purchased for the original fixture – which was due to take place on Sunday 22 January before being postponed – will be valid for the rearranged date.
The match will be broadcast live on Sky Sports and further ticket information will be confirmed by Brighton & Hove Albion in due course.
